Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,またか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I try again and again, to no avail.
